title: Aaron Rodgers, Antonio Brown, Virginia, and the Cowboys
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, Antonio Brown, Virginia, and the Cowboys
description:
Colin breaks down Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers' rebuttal, the continued drama surrounding Oakland Raiders WR Antonio Brown, Virginia's win over Texas Tech, and why he feels Dallas Cowboys QB Dak Prescott will get his money. Guests include Michael Lewis, Aaron Torres, Chris Hayes, and Greg Jennings.
